        "created_at": "2015-12-16T16:26:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Had this for dinner last night\u2026  Pop and Poured\u2026   On the nose there was slights hints of lemon zest and some floral notes (lavendar?) coming thru.  On the palate the wine was very mineral driven with faint lemon oil and stone fruit character.  The acidity was rather high for this wine and it made for a lingering finish.</p>\n<p>Very good not great</p>",
