        "cooked": "<blockquote>\n<p>Very good not great</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Well, or too young - or not enough air ?</p>\n<p>I had the 2006 Village some weeks ago, and it was spectacular for a Village wine, but after careful preparation with slow ox and decanting</p>",
