        "created_at": "2015-12-16T18:00:37.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>In my experience I\u2019d tentatively suggest that 2006 was one of Coche\u2019s less successful vintages, with the wines lacking just a bit of their usual magic. Would be interested to hear what others have to say.</p>",
